## Limitations

The analysis is based on available online resources, which may not cover all perspectives or the most recent developments in the Syrian conflict. Additionally, the complexity of the war means that some nuances and local factors might not be fully captured in this report. Further research, including field studies and interviews with stakeholders, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the conflict's causes.